<paragraph blockId="22.[151,1437,152,576]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,285,152,179]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Colour.</emphasis>
Black. Tegula brown. Palpi and spurs pale yellowish. Antenna and ovipositor sheath dark brown. Labrum and mandible dark brown. Legs brown, except fore leg, most part of middle femur, middle tibia with tarsus, basal two-third of hind tibia with basal half of hind basitarsus yellow. Wing membrane hyaline, C+SC+R, 1-R1, pterostigma, r, 2-SR and 2-M yellowish brown, the rest more or less pale brown.
</paragraph>
